data.description: Access to Carriere's only gated lake community? Yes, please! Living here is a LIFESTYLE; fishing, swimming, and boating are in your future when you own this beautiful when you own this huge 3 bedroom, 2 bath home! Boasting 2,150 ft of living space, and 2,880 sf of total under beam — this house is ROOMY! And walking distance to the front recreation area. Upon approach you'll notice a lush yard and the coziest front porch stretching the length of the home. Upon entry, you'll be greeted with the living room with a wood burning fireplace, and the dining room — both of which are covered in windows. The primary suite, and kitchen are on the first floor. The primary suite has double vanities, double closets, and a separate tub and shower. The second floor offers 2 bedrooms and a full guest bathroom. Throughout the upstairs area of the home, you'll find lots of bonus storage space built in — a thoughtful touch from the original owner. The rear porch offers an equally relaxing environment, and connects to the carport (no more wet heads on rainy days). The Hide A Way community offers a pool, club house, 2 parks, 2 marinas, walking and exercise areas and so much more. This home is move-in ready and available for showings today. Quick access to front gate! With 1 hour to the Miss. Gulf Coast and 45 minutes New Orleans, LA, this is a popular spot for locals, commuters, and second home owners. Special note: Hide A Way is a private and gated subdivision. You can access all information about the HOA at www.hawlms.com. You are allowed to park boats, trailers, campers, golf carts and other types of vehicles and toys in your driveway or in the rear part of your property.
